## Special Scenarios

### Design System Update (batch changes)
- Multiple components affected
- All snapshot failures
- **Recommendation:** Batch update after review

### Storybook/Stencil Upgrade
- Package.json version bumps
- Snapshot format may change
- **Recommendation:** Update snapshots

### Test Refactoring
- Only `.stories.ts` files changed
- No component changes
- **Recommendation:** Fix test logic

